parameters:
???: "...All I can do has come to an end... From here on
out, at Orca Mountain... as the right hand of Mayor Orca,
I'll give my full support! As the mayor's secretary and a
ruthless monster... I'll cast aside my emotions and fight!!"

Drillmaid: "Drill-drill~!! In just a few hours, it's Monster
Fight time!! The winner will be Mayor Orca... without a
doubt... that little girl is bound to lose!"

Drillmaid: "From tomorrow, Dirtgain City will enter a true
era of darkness... It's not just about the tasty powder...
all the dark organizations will be gone, and a reign of
terror solely for the mayor will be established!"

Drillmaid: "...Little girl... I won't cheer for you... but
if you truly are the successor to Shark Broccoli... his
heart... no..."
